author: The Critical Drinker
description: Could the failure of Ballerina be a symptom of a much larger problem in Hollywood? Why did Scarlett Johansson have her name removed from Thunderbolts? And with Mark Hamill stepping away from Star Wars for good, what will his legacy be? Join me, MauLer, Razorfist, Disparu, Robot Head and Filmcomicsexplained for Open Bar 146.
title: Open Bar #146 - Hollywood's Girlboss Fatigue, Mark Hamill Ditches Star Wars, Black Widow Snub
